data.description: Unveil potential in this Stuart, FL condo in KingsWood Community. Awaiting your touch, envision crafting a coastal haven minutes from beaches and restaurants. This canvas for renovation is not one to pass up.Picture mornings on Ocean Club Golf Course, 8 minutes away, followed by afternoons on sandy shores. 15 minutes to downtown Stuart, a vibrant hub of entertainment and vistas. In this caring community, neighbors become friends, adding warmth to your retreat.Beyond walls, Florida's spirit invites you to join clubs, connecting with kindred spirits. Despite renovation, it's more than a property; it's a gateway to paradise. Seize the opportunity to own a piece of Florida's charm, where your dream home awaits transformation into a coastal masterpiece. Live where others Vacation!
